be reversed','1111-11-11','Admin','Experiencing course list issues','Tech','Resolve','2018-06-20 02:15:24','2018-06-21 00:04:21'),(162,'','AC Update 2.14.0.55','2018-06-11','Justeen Mae Arandia','<h2>1. 1v1 kid classroom interface optimization</h2>\r\n<p>Cancel unnecessary feature：</p>\r\n<p>1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Switch channel</p>\r\n<p>2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Speaker/microphone volume setting</p>\r\n<p>3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Device detection</p>\r\n<p>4)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Quick fix</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Optimize interactive experience：</p>\r\n<p>1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Intelligence tip way （keep the same way with 1vMore classroom）</p>\r\n<p>2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Video operation relate feature</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/photos/9/AC Teacher.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"630\" height=\"373\" /></p>\r\n<h2>2. The teacher end feature:Enlarge video window</h2>\r\n<p>This feature only works at teacher end，the teacher only enlarge themselves video window</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/photos/9/2.14 window.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"627\" height=\"371\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/photos/9/2.14 window_large.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"626\" height=\"371\" /></p>\r\n<h2>3. The teacher end feature:CPU &amp; Memory usage indication</h2>\r\n<p>After entering classroom，AC detects the usage of CPU/Memory，if the usage of CPU/Memory is high will tip the teacher</p>\r\n<p>Click &ldquo;Low Power Mode&rdquo;，AC will shut up &ldquo;video decoration/noise reduction/audio detection&rdquo; feature automatically</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/photos/9/2.14 Low power.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"626\" height=\"371\" /></p>\r\n<h2>4. Text Mode Tip</h2>\r\n<p>If config &ldquo;testmode&rdquo; file test ,the interface will appear this tip</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/photos/9/2.14 testmode.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"626\" height=\"407\" /></p>\r\n<h2>5. Fix Bug</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>fixed the crash caused by teacher side enable record</li>\r\n<li>the crash caused by quitting AC</li>\r\n<li>CEF module crash in the classroom</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><em>This crash may be caused by the computer&nbsp;itself</em></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/photos/9/2.14 bug.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"635\" height=\"376\" /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Cannot See next page button</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img src=\"/photos/9/2.14 bug2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"635\" height=\"337\" /></p>','Downtime Advisory','Active','2018-06-10 22:42:02','2018-06-10 22:42:02'),(164,'','Start time: 20:00','1111-11-11','Erwyne Herreria','Ac Course List issues Ongoing, we are receiving high volume on the issue, all penalties regarding this issue will automatically  be reversed.  No need to submit fees disputes for reversal','Tech','Resolve','2018-06-18 22:00:48','2018-06-21 05:38:33');
